data.description: Embrace boundless possibilities on this 5-acre unrestricted haven. This pristine plot of land offers the perfect blend of space, comfort, and natural beauty. Behind the main 4 bed 2 bath home there are a plethora of bonuses, like the second water and electric hookup, ready for your guest house or future expansion plans. Plus, with numerous new construction homes sprouting up all around, your investment in this property is poised for even greater potential. Not only is there one, but two chicken coops along with two storage sheds for all of your equipment! Complete with a double gate entry your dream retreat awaits!
